1. Simply approach the instructor personally if you have any comments and feedback on the course. If possible, please make an appointment before you come.
2. Sent an email to the instructor (kmcheng@phy.cuhk.edu.hk), give the instructor a call (3943 4076), or come to instructor’s office; especially for issues that require immediate action;
3. express your views in the course evaluation;
4. express your views (or ask a student representative to help you convey the messages) in the staff-student consultation meeting held every year.

